=3D"1:1-1:173">That phrase, "the one-eyed purple pill eater," evokes a surr=
eal and somewhat unsettling image. It's open to interpretation, but here ar=
e some possible ways to understand it:</p><ul data-sourcepos=3D"3:1-14:0">
<li data-sourcepos=3D"3:1-7:148"><strong>Symbolism:</strong>
<ul data-sourcepos=3D"4:5-7:148">
<li data-sourcepos=3D"4:5-4:68">"One-eyed" could represent a limited or dis=
torted perspective.</li>
<li data-sourcepos=3D"5:5-5:80">"Purple" often symbolizes something unusual=
, mystical, or even artificial.</li>
<li data-sourcepos=3D"6:5-6:111">"Pill eater" could refer to someone who co=
nsumes something that alters their perception or state of mind.</li>
<li data-sourcepos=3D"7:5-7:148">Therefore the entire phrase could refer to=
 a person that has a distorted perception of reality due to consumption of =
mind altering substances.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-sourcepos=3D"8:1-10:99"><strong>Literary/Creative:</strong>
<ul data-sourcepos=3D"9:5-10:99">
<li data-sourcepos=3D"9:5-9:103">It could be a fragment of a story, poem, o=
r song, intended to create a vivid and memorable image.</li>
<li data-sourcepos=3D"10:5-10:99">It has a fantastical quality, suggesting =
a character from a science fiction or fantasy world.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-sourcepos=3D"11:1-14:0"><strong>Abstract:</strong>
<ul data-sourcepos=3D"12:5-14:0">
<li data-sourcepos=3D"12:5-12:116">It could represent an abstract concept, =
such as the way technology or media can distort our view of the world.</li>
<li data-sourcepos=3D"13:5-14:0">It could be a metaphor for someone who is =
consumed by a single idea, or belief.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul><p data-sourcepos=3D"15:1-15:89">Essentially it is a very interesting =
string of words, that creates a strong mental image.</p></div></message-con=
